Interface ISerialiserVocab

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FSerialiserVocab
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ISerialiserVocab
extends FSerialiserVocab
    Vocabulary for the standard XML serialisation of MEKON instances. Extends FSerialiserVocab in order to incorporate vocabulary for the standard XML serialisation of frames model entities.
